node.text: This has probably been one of my favorite trips fishing in Venice Louisiana!!! These oil rigs just amazes me it’s a different world out here and I love getting the opportunity to come experience all the different fishing Venice has to offer. If u haven’t been here I’d definitely recommend it you won’t be disappointed... Book a trip Come out bring the family, kids, friends & enjoy the fun!!! @southerncatchoutfitters @landonbjohnson07

node.text:
Getting to spend time in the Woods with Family and Friends is what it’s all about🙏🏼 So thankful for the crew over at @floutdoors for making this such a memorable weekend for me and my family. After Jase & my Daddy getting there Turkey it was my turn to give a ol Long Beard a dirt nap... Thank you @captgd & @oldsouth_angler for this exciting hunt!!! 
#floutdoors #cantstoptheflop #turkeyhunting #goodtimes #goodfriends #greatmemories

node.title: These are the moments that make me so happy🦃

Love showing & teaching the kids the whole process of harvesting our animals... A few days ago we trapped some hogs in our @hogg.boss.gates to make us some sausage that will last us all year long. Growing up always processing our own games with my parents makes me happy to pass the leaning experiences on to my kids💖💙 
#proudhunter #processing #wildgame #hog #sausage #knowwhereyourmeatcomesfrom #raisedright

node.text: This excitement makes my heart so happy!!!! Love that my kids are so thankful and love the outdoors and hunting as much as I do💖💙🙏🏼 @dbfirearms made them the perfect 300 blackouts and how special are these with there names engraved on them!!! Can’t wait for all the memorable hunts they will make with these Diamondbacks🐗🦌

node.text: This has probably been one of my favorite trips fishing in Venice Louisiana!!! These oil rigs just amazes me it’s a different world out here and I love getting the opportunity to come experience all the different fishing Venice has to offer. If u haven’t been here I’d definitely recommend it you won’t be disappointed... Book a trip Come out bring the family, kids, friends & enjoy the fun!!! @southerncatchoutfitters @landonbjohnson07
